		- www.jscache.com.edgesuite.net


	Other TripAdvisor rulesets:

		- VirtualTourist.xml


	Nonfunctional tripadvisor.com subdomains:

		- cobrands **
		- flights *	(mismatched, CN: *.seatguru.com)
		- flights-cdn ***
		- ir
		- no *
		- pl *
		- th ***
		- tripwow *
		- tuiuk **
